  "What is a 'vector'?": "什么是\"维多\"?",
  "A quantity that has only magnitude": "数量数量只有数量大小",
  "A line segment with no specified direction": "没有指定方向的直线段",
  "A quantity that has both magnitude and direction": "既具有规模又具有方向的数量",
  "A point in the coordinate plane": "坐标平面的一个点",
  "A vector is a mathematical quantity that has both magnitude (size/length) and direction. Examples include velocity, force, and displacement.": "矢量是一种具有数值(大小/长度)和方向的数学数量,例如速度、力和移位。",
  "What is a 'scalar' in the context of vectors?": "矢量的“ 梯度” 是什么 ?",
  "A quantity with both magnitude and direction": "数量,包括数量和方向",
  "The terminal point of a vector": "矢量的终点点",
  "The angle of a vector": "矢量角度",
  "A real number that has magnitude only, used to multiply vectors": "用于乘向量的真实数字, 仅具有大小, 用于乘向量",
  "A scalar is a single real number with magnitude only (no direction). When a scalar multiplies a vector, it changes the vector's magnitude (and possibly reverses its direction).": "标量是一个只有星级( 无方向) 的单个真实数字。 当标量乘以矢量时, 它会改变矢量的大小( 并可能逆转方向 ) 。",
  "What does 'magnitude' of a vector mean?": "矢量的“ 宏大” 意味着什么 ?",
  "The direction the vector points": "向量点的方向",
  "The length or size of the vector, calculated as √(a² + b²) for vector ⟨a, b⟩": "矢量的长度或大小,计算为 (a2 + b2) 的矢量 a, b 的矢量的长度或大小。",
  "The dot product of the vector with itself": "矢量本身的点产物",
  "The x-component of the vector": "矢量的 x 组成部分",
  "The magnitude (or norm) of a vector ⟨a, b⟩ is its length: |v| = √(a² + b²). It is always a non-negative scalar value.": "矢量 a, b 的大小( 或规范) 是它的长度 :\\ v = ( a2 + b2) 。 它总是非负的天平值 。",
  "What is a 'unit vector'?": "什么是“单位矢量”?",
  "A vector that points in the direction of the x-axis": "指向 X 轴方向的矢量",
  "Any vector with positive components": "含有正成分的任何矢量",
  "A vector with a magnitude of exactly 1": "精确度为 1 的矢量",
  "The first vector in a set of vectors": "一组矢量中的第一个矢量",
  "A unit vector has a magnitude of 1. It indicates direction only. Any nonzero vector v can be made into a unit vector by dividing by its magnitude: v/|v|.": "单位矢量的大小为 1, 它只表示方向。 任何非零矢量 v 都可以除以其大小 : v/ v , 制成单位矢量 。",
  "What does the 'dot product' of two vectors represent?": "两个矢量的“ 点产物” 代表什么 ?",
  "A scalar value equal to the sum of the products of corresponding components": "等值于相应组件产品总和的标值",
  "The area of the parallelogram formed by the two vectors": "由两个矢量构成的平行图区域区域",
  "A vector perpendicular to both input vectors": "与两个输入矢量都对应的矢量",
  "The average of the two vectors": "两个矢量的平均值",
