  "What does 'orthogonal' mean for two vectors?": "对于两个矢量,“ orthogoal” 意味着什么 ?",
  "The vectors have the same magnitude": "矢量的量与矢量的量值相同",
  "The vectors are parallel": "矢量是平行的",
  "The vectors point in the same direction": "矢量指向同一方向",
  "The vectors are perpendicular to each other (their dot product is zero)": "矢量相互垂直(其点值产品为零)",
  "Orthogonal vectors are perpendicular, forming a 90° angle. The algebraic test is that their dot product equals zero: u · v = 0.": "矩形矢量为垂直直角,形成90度角。代数测试是,它们的点值产品等于零: u / v = 0。",
  "What is a 'resultant vector'?": "什么是“结果矢量”?",
