  "The difference between two vectors": "两个矢量之间的差异",
  "The unit vector of the sum": "和的单位矢量",
  "The vector sum of two or more vectors, representing their combined effect": "两个或两个以上矢量的矢量总和,代表其综合效应",
  "The resultant vector is obtained by adding two or more vectors. It represents the combined effect, such as the net force when multiple forces act on an object.": "生成的矢量是通过添加两个或两个以上矢量获得的。它代表合并效应,如多重力对物体采取行动时的净力。",
  "What does 'component form' of a vector mean?": "矢量的“ 构件形式” 意味着什么 ?",
