  "Drawing the vector on a graph": "在图形上绘制矢量",
  "Component form expresses a vector as ⟨a, b⟩, where a is the horizontal (x) component and b is the vertical (y) component.": "构件窗体表示矢量为 a, b,其中a为水平(x)构件,b为垂直(y)构件。",
