  "What does 'scalar multiplication' do to a vector?": "向量的“ 日历乘法” 对向量有什么作用 ?",
  "It adds a constant to each component": "在每个组成部分中增加一个常数",
  "It rotates the vector by the scalar amount": "它以计算数量旋转矢量",
