  "It changes the direction but not the magnitude": "它会改变方向,但不会改变规模",
  "Multiplying a vector by a positive scalar changes its magnitude but keeps its direction. A negative scalar reverses the direction. The result is k⟨a, b⟩ = ⟨ka, kb⟩.": "将矢量乘以正弧值会改变其大小, 但会保持方向。 负弧值会逆转方向 。 结果是 ka, b = ka, kb 。",
