  "Two forces act on an object: F₁ = ⟨8, 6⟩ N and F₂ = ⟨-3, 4⟩ N. A physics student needs the magnitude of the resultant force. What is it?": "F1 = 8, 6N 和 F2 = - 3, 4N. 物理学学生需要由此产生的力量的大小。 它是什么?",
