  "A crane lifts a load with two cables making angles with the vertical. Cable 1 has tension T₁ = ⟨-300, 400⟩ N and Cable 2 has tension T₂ = ⟨300, 400⟩ N. Are the horizontal components balanced?": "一台起重机抬起一个负荷,用两条电缆从垂直角度制造角。 1号电缆的张力T1 = -300, 400N和2号电缆的张力T2 = 300, 400N。 横向部件平衡吗?",
